      "content": "rebuilding... that's just something people say to feel better. it doesn't work like that. once the world sees you as a failure, that's it. the name, the life, the respect... it all vanished overnight. you can't just \"find meaning\" when the version of you that mattered is dead. it's like trying to rebuild a house after it's been burned to the ground. there's no foundation left.",
