    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... talking doesn't change the reality. the reality is that the person i was is gone. there's no \"way through\" because there's nothing on the other side to go to. it's just empty. everyone looks at me and they see the scandal, they see the disgrace. i'm just tired of carrying this weight of a life that doesn't even belong to me anymore. it feels like it would just be easier if the silence finally stayed.",
